{"article_id":"akHyAUXSVsHXCDwT","edus":[{"id":0,"text":"North Korea has said","depth":2},{"id":1,"text":"it may pull out of a summit with US President Donald Trump","depth":3},{"id":2,"text":"if the US insists","depth":4},{"id":3,"text":"it gives up its nuclear weapons unilaterally .","depth":4},{"id":4,"text":"The highly anticipated meeting between Mr Trump and North Korea 's Kim Jong-un is due to take place on 12 June .","depth":4},{"id":5,"text":"But in an angry statement , North Korea 's vice-foreign minister accused the US of making reckless statements","depth":7},{"id":6,"text":"and of harbouring sinister intentions .","depth":7},{"id":7,"text":"He pointed the finger squarely at US National Security Adviser John Bolton .","depth":6},{"id":8,"text":"`` We do not hide our feeling of repugnance towards him , ''","depth":6},{"id":9,"text":"Kim Kye-gwan said .","depth":6},{"id":10,"text":"The White House has responded","depth":5},{"id":11,"text":"by saying","depth":6},{"id":12,"text":"it is still hopeful","depth":7},{"id":13,"text":"the meeting will go ahead .","depth":7},{"id":14,"text":"`` The president is ready","depth":7},{"id":15,"text":"if the meeting takes place .","depth":7},{"id":16,"text":"If it does n't ,","depth":7},{"id":17,"text":"we 'll continue the maximum pressure campaign","depth":8},{"id":18,"text":"that 's been ongoing , ''","depth":8},{"id":19,"text":"said spokesperson Sarah Sanders .","depth":5},{"id":20,"text":"The groundbreaking agreement","depth":10},{"id":21,"text":"for Mr Kim and Mr Trump to meet","depth":10},{"id":22,"text":"came about","depth":9},{"id":23,"text":"as North Korea said","depth":9},{"id":24,"text":"it was committed to denuclearising the Korean peninsula .","depth":9},{"id":25,"text":"Exactly what that would entail has remained unclear ,","depth":8},{"id":26,"text":"but North Korea has invited foreign media to witness the dismantling of its main nuclear test site later this month .","depth":8},{"id":27,"text":"Mr Bolton recently said","depth":8},{"id":28,"text":"North Korea could follow a `` Libya model '' of verifiable denuclearisation ,","depth":9},{"id":29,"text":"but this alarms Pyongyang ,","depth":10},{"id":30,"text":"which watched Libya 's Colonel Gaddafi give up his nuclear programme","depth":11},{"id":31,"text":"only for him to be killed by Western-backed rebels a few years later .","depth":11},{"id":32,"text":"The BBC 's Laura Bicker in Seoul says","depth":12},{"id":33,"text":"North Korea","depth":14},{"id":34,"text":"- which had long said","depth":15},{"id":35,"text":"its nuclear arsenal is essential for its survival as a state -","depth":15},{"id":36,"text":"is now making its demands clear .","depth":13},{"id":37,"text":"The whole reason","depth":15},{"id":38,"text":"it has spent years","depth":16},{"id":39,"text":"building up a nuclear arsenal , at such a great cost ,","depth":16},{"id":40,"text":"is for survival .","depth":14},{"id":41,"text":"So to compare denuclearisation in North Korea with Libya or indeed Iraq","depth":15},{"id":42,"text":"as John Bolton did on Sunday","depth":15},{"id":43,"text":"is not going to offer much comfort .","depth":14},{"id":44,"text":"Both regimes collapsed .","depth":12},{"id":45,"text":"This is also a warning shot to the Trump administration .","depth":11},{"id":46,"text":"They will be aware how much Mr Trump wants this summit","depth":12},{"id":47,"text":"and how it is being spun as a success","depth":13},{"id":48,"text":"brought about by his maximum pressure strategy .","depth":13},{"id":49,"text":"There were signs","depth":11},{"id":50,"text":"this boasting irritated Pyongyang ,","depth":11},{"id":51,"text":"but now it has decided to speak out through someone in a position of power .","depth":10},{"id":52,"text":"North Korea wants the world to know","depth":12},{"id":53,"text":"that it is coming to the negotiating table from a position of strength ,","depth":12},{"id":54,"text":"and they may feel","depth":12},{"id":55,"text":"that they are making all the concessions .","depth":12},{"id":56,"text":"They 've suspended all missile tests ,","depth":11},{"id":57,"text":"released the three US detainees ,","depth":12},{"id":58,"text":"Kim Jong-un met President Moon","depth":14},{"id":59,"text":"and the pair signed a declaration ,","depth":14},{"id":60,"text":"and they 're about to dismantle a nuclear test site in front of international media .","depth":13},{"id":61,"text":"So to hear the Trump administration claiming credit for a deal","depth":11},{"id":62,"text":"they do n't like","depth":11},{"id":63,"text":"has been a step too far .","depth":10},{"id":64,"text":"These statements more than hint","depth":6},{"id":65,"text":"that North Korea is prepared to walk away from President Trump 's summit in Singapore","depth":7},{"id":66,"text":"until it does hear a deal","depth":8},{"id":67,"text":"it does like .","depth":8},{"id":68,"text":"Mr Kim 's statement ,","depth":9},{"id":69,"text":"carried by state media ,","depth":9},{"id":70,"text":"said","depth":8},{"id":71,"text":"that","depth":8},{"id":72,"text":"if the US `` corners us","depth":10},{"id":73,"text":"and unilaterally demands","depth":11},{"id":74,"text":"we give up nuclear weapons","depth":11},{"id":75,"text":"we will no longer have an interest in talks ''","depth":10},{"id":76,"text":"and `` will have to reconsider '' attending the 12 June summit in Singapore .","depth":10},{"id":77,"text":"He said","depth":7},{"id":78,"text":"North Korea did have `` high hopes ''","depth":8},{"id":79,"text":"but that it was `` very unfortunate that the US is provoking us ahead of the summit","depth":9},{"id":80,"text":"by spitting out ludicrous statements '' .","depth":9},{"id":81,"text":"Kim Kye-gwan is known to be highly respected in the North Korean leadership","depth":7},{"id":82,"text":"and has taken part in negotiations with the US before .","depth":7},{"id":83,"text":"There is very little chance","depth":7},{"id":84,"text":"his comments were not personally endorsed by Kim Jong-un .","depth":7},{"id":85,"text":"Hours before the announcement , in a sign of growing problems , North Korea had also pulled out of a meeting","depth":8},{"id":86,"text":"scheduled with South Korea on Wednesday .","depth":8},{"id":87,"text":"because of anger over the start of US-South Korea joint military drills .","depth":7},{"id":88,"text":"North Korea had earlier said","depth":8},{"id":89,"text":"it would allow them to go ahead ,","depth":8},{"id":90,"text":"but then called them `` a provocative military ruckus ''","depth":8},{"id":91,"text":"which was undermining its diplomatic efforts .","depth":8},{"id":92,"text":"The sudden change in tone from Pyongyang is said to have taken US officials by surprise .","depth":7},{"id":93,"text":"Analysts said","depth":8},{"id":94,"text":"North Korea could be trying to strengthen its hand before talks .","depth":8},{"id":95,"text":"The US state department said","depth":7},{"id":96,"text":"it was continuing to plan the Trump-Kim meeting ,","depth":8},{"id":97,"text":"and Mr Trump is yet to comment .","depth":8},{"id":98,"text":"A Chinese government spokesman urged North Korea and the US to `` meet each other halfway '' ahead of negotiations .","depth":5},{"id":99,"text":"The hawkish conservative is a firm defender of US power and a confrontational advocate","depth":10},{"id":100,"text":"for wielding that strength abroad .","depth":10},{"id":101,"text":"He has previously said","depth":10},{"id":102,"text":"it would be `` perfectly legitimate '' to carry out a pre-emptive strike on North Korea .","depth":10},{"id":103,"text":"In media interviews over the weekend , he said","depth":10},{"id":104,"text":"North Korea could follow a Libyan model of nuclear disarmament","depth":10},{"id":105,"text":"-","depth":10},{"id":106,"text":"Libya gave up its weapons ' programmes in the early 2000s","depth":12},{"id":107,"text":"and only then secured economic aid","depth":13},{"id":108,"text":"and normalised relations with the US .","depth":13},{"id":109,"text":"However during the 2011 uprising against Colonel Gaddafi 's regime , Western powers intervened in Libya in favour of the rebels ,","depth":12},{"id":110,"text":"and Gaddafi was captured","depth":13},{"id":111,"text":"and killed .","depth":13},{"id":112,"text":"North Korea has in the past suggested","depth":8},{"id":113,"text":"that Libya may have escaped Western military intervention","depth":9},{"id":114,"text":"had it kept its nuclear weapons programme .","depth":9},{"id":115,"text":"Kim Kye-gwan said in his statement","depth":8},{"id":116,"text":"that this was `` not an expression of intention","depth":10},{"id":117,"text":"to address the issue through dialogue '' .","depth":10},{"id":118,"text":"`` It is essentially a manifestation of awfully sinister moves","depth":10},{"id":119,"text":"to impose on our dignified state the destiny of Libya or Iraq","depth":11},{"id":120,"text":"which had been collapsed","depth":12},{"id":121,"text":"due to yielding the whole of their countries to big powers . `` We do not hide our feeling of repugnance towards [ Bolton ] . ''","depth":12},{"id":122,"text":"Mr Kim also warns Mr Trump","depth":8},{"id":123,"text":"that","depth":9},{"id":124,"text":"if he `` follows in the footsteps of his predecessors ''","depth":11},{"id":125,"text":"- refusing to engage with North Korea","depth":12},{"id":126,"text":"unless it gives up its nuclear weapons -","depth":12},{"id":127,"text":"`` he will be recorded as more tragic and unsuccessful president than his predecessors , far from his initial ambition","depth":11},{"id":128,"text":"to make unprecedented success '' .","depth":11}],"relations":[{"parent":257,"left":132,"right":256,"relation":"joint","nuclearity":"NN"},{"parent":132,"left":0,"right":131,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},{"parent":131,"left":1,"right":130,"relation":"condition","nuclearity":"NS"},{"parent":130,"left":2,"right":3,"relation":"attribution","nuclearity":"SN"},